author: Suhas Nayse
title: Nagpur district selection trials for state aquatics on Wednesday
text:
NAGPUR: The Nagpur District Amateur Aquatic Association will hold the selection trials to select the Nagpur district squad for the 77th Senior State Swimming, Diving and Water Polo Championship on September 30 (Wednesday) here at the Kamgar Kalyan Raghuji Nagar Swimming Pool at 7:30 pm.
The state aquatics competition will be held October 10 and 11. On the basis of performance in the selection trials, district team will be declared.
The NDAAA secretary Sambhaji Bhonsale, joint secretary Rameshwar Likhar and Nitin Yemde can be contacted for more details.
